Pronounce the blessing over barley and corn. In the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost. Boil it and bring it...37 through the merit of Esau,38 of Moses, of [xxxviii] David,39 of Solomon, of Gabriel, the great Angel,40 peace be upon him! With a loud voice throw41 with sixty-six42 ounces (?)43 towards the sky,44 each ounce(?)45 . . . . . . . .46 Crush frankincense, cry (?)47 BLN, BLN, CLN, CLN. Break upon them (the sounds) BIGU, BIGU, BIGANA,48 JRJI, JRJI, JRJANA,49 from a grunting reed \f1\emdash  a clear, swelling torrent,50 drawing out the trumpet-sound (?)51 of effective extermination52 from off him who bears this charm, Amen!\par
