\'a7 22. BINDING THE EVIL APPARITION.\par
In the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost. My brother Moses \f1\emdash  the servant of God \emdash  was tending the sheep between seven mountains,58 and there met him three evil forms: one was an evil man, (the other) an evil wolf, and (the third) an evil lion.\par
