[xl] In the name of the Father, may the evil man be bound by me; in the name of the Son, may the evil wolf be bound by me; in the name or the Holy Ghost, may the evil lion be bound by me, so that they may not approach the person, nor the house of him who beareth these writs, through the prayer of the Virgin Mary. Amen!\par
