\'a7 3. THE PRAYER OF THE HOLY ANGELS.\par
O holy God, holy Mighty One, holy Immortal: O our Lord, have pity upon us: O our Lord, receive thou our petition: O our Lord, be gracious unto thy servants who bear these writs (amulets). Amen!\par
